<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472672' id='t-472672'>went from the bottom of their district
to the top,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479471' id='t-479471'>and that district included
affluent sections of Seattle.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='485193' id='t-485193'>So the native kids outdid
the Microsoft kids.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:23
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492484' id='t-492484'>This happened because the meaning</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='495731' id='t-495731'>of effort and difficulty were transformed.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500368' id='t-500368'>Before, effort and difficulty</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504800' id='t-504800'>made them feel dumb,
