<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517203' id='t-517203'>stronger connections.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518968' id='t-518968'>That's when they're getting smarter.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='522509' id='t-522509'>I received a letter recently
